reviewText: My grand daughter and I love this tape, is captures her attention the songs are very nice that get her dancing and singing. Unfortualtely, the Joji site is unconstuction. We hope and pray that they make more dvd's with Joji and a stuffed animal. She watches it all year long, even though it's a Christmas dvd. Please make more or tell me where to get more products for a little girl who loves Joji
